content: avaer: Made significant code cleanup with PR #3346 removing plugin imports from agent (-629 lines), while also contributing three smaller fixes including adding SQLite adapter support (#3357) and addressing character loading issues (#3374, #3375). Activity was sporadic across just 4 days this month, but resulted in substantial codebase changes totaling +12,865/-26,400 lines across 42 commits, primarily focused on other work (69%) and feature development (19%).
